\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\"/>\n</p>\n\n---\n\n## 🔗 Support & Links\n\n- 💬 **Discord:** https://discord.gg/TJc3CxR4jK  \n- 💻 **GitHub:** https://github.com/MeherBenSalem  \n- 🔥 **CurseForge:** https://www.curseforge.com/members/nightbeamstudio/projects  \n- 🧩 **Modrinth:** https://modrinth.com/organization/nightbeam  \n\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/nightbeam\">\n    <img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/db9c3eef-25e8-4ac0-93b6-bf386644dcef.webp\" alt=\"BisectHosting partner banner\" />\n  </a>\n</p>",
